---
title: SpacesSync — C4 Level 3 (Component) — roadmap with config layer + settings pane
---
flowchart TB
    classDef public fill:#1168bd,stroke:#0e5aa7,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef internal fill:#438dd5,stroke:#2e6da4,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef proposed fill:#2e7d32,stroke:#4caf50,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 4 2
    classDef external fill:#999,stroke:#666,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef config fill:#5a4a1e,stroke:#d4a853,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef store fill:#3a2d52,stroke:#7b5fb0,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px

    User([User]):::public

    subgraph Spoon [SpacesSync.spoon]
        API[Public API<br/>:start :stop :toggle<br/>:openSettings ＊new＊<br/>:bindHotkeys]:::public

        subgraph Engine [Existing engine]
            Watcher[Watcher<br/>hs.spaces.watcher]:::internal
            SyncEng[Sync Engine<br/>chained gotoSpace<br/>+ debounce]:::internal
            PosMap[Position Map<br/>UUID ↔ position]:::internal
            GroupLook[Group Lookup<br/>getTargetsFor]:::internal
            Names[Name Store<br/>per-group<br/>Space names]:::internal
            UI[Popup / Picker /<br/>Status HUD<br/>hs.canvas + eventtap]:::internal
        end

        subgraph New [Proposed]
            ConfigMod[Config Module<br/>config.lua<br/>load / save / validate<br/>pathwatcher<br/>groupOf ↔ syncGroups]:::proposed
            SettingsPane[Settings Pane<br/>hs.webview<br/>HTML form + JS bridge]:::proposed
            ScreenWatch[Screen Watcher<br/>hs.screen.watcher<br/>＊new＊ writes _lastSeen<br/>on disconnect]:::proposed
        end
    end

    JSON[("SpacesSync.json<br/>~/.hammerspoon/<br/><br/>＊canonical config＊<br/>enabled, syncMode, groupOf,<br/>groupLabels, spaceNames,<br/>_lastSeen — name, uuid, date, wasIn<br/>switchDelay, debounceSeconds,<br/>popupDuration, statusDuration,<br/>hotkeys")]:::config
    Plist[(hs.settings plist<br/><br/>＊legacy＊<br/>pre-v3 Space names<br/>read once on first run,<br/>migrated into JSON spaceNames,<br/>then ignored)]:::store
    HSAPIs[Hammerspoon APIs<br/>hs.spaces hs.screen hs.screen.watcher<br/>hs.canvas hs.webview<br/>hs.pathwatcher hs.json<br/>hs.shutdownCallback]:::external

    Shutdown[hs.shutdownCallback<br/>＊new＊ teardown<br/>delete webview<br/>unsubscribe userContent<br/>stop pathwatcher]:::proposed

    User -->|hotkeys| API
    User -->|opens| SettingsPane
    User -->|hand-edits| JSON

    API -->|on :start: seed,<br/>load, applyToSpoon,<br/>startWatching| ConfigMod
    API -->|reads runtime fields<br/>populated by config| Engine
    SettingsPane <-->|JS↔Lua<br/>loadState applyState| ConfigMod

    ConfigMod -->|reads/writes<br/>SHA-256 ring buffer<br/>echo suppression| JSON
    ConfigMod -->|watches parent dir<br/>filters by basename<br/>retries on parse fail| JSON
    ConfigMod -->|on groupOf change<br/>migrate keys atomically<br/>flag orphans| Names

    SettingsPane -->|register| Shutdown
    ConfigMod -->|register| Shutdown

    ScreenWatch -->|on disconnect:<br/>writeLastSeen| ConfigMod
    ScreenWatch -->|on connect:<br/>rebuildPositionMap| Engine

    Watcher -->|fires on Space change| SyncEng
    SyncEng --> GroupLook
    GroupLook --> PosMap
    SyncEng --> UI
    Names --> UI
    Names -->|read by| ConfigMod
    ConfigMod -->|spaceNames live in JSON now,<br/>Plist is migration-source only| JSON

    Engine --> HSAPIs
    UI --> HSAPIs
    ConfigMod --> HSAPIs
    SettingsPane --> HSAPIs

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend [Legend]
        direction LR
        L1[existing]:::internal
        L2[proposed]:::proposed
    end
